sentences.english: Maybe some newsy remembers an odd customer.
sentences.chinese: 也许哪个卖报的还记得这么个古怪的顾客。

sentences.english: From which dynasty was the blue---flower porcelain plate in the Hall of Happiness and Longevity left?
sentences.chinese: 颐和园乐寿堂内的青花大磁盘是哪个朝代的遗物？

sentences.english: Which typeface is perfect for this design?
sentences.chinese: 哪个字体最适合这个设计？

sentences.english: Which one would you like first?
Which classes benefit most from Jewelcrafting?
sentences.chinese: 哪个职业将会从宝石学中受益最大？

sentences.english: A. Which program impresses you the most during the Spring Festival Evening Gala last night?
sentences.chinese: 昨天春晚的哪个节目你印象最深刻？

sentences.english: Can you show me where I am in this map?
sentences.chinese: 你能告诉我我现在处于地图上的哪个位置吗？

sentences.english: We need a sentence letter, what should we have?
sentences.chinese: 我们与要一个句子的字母，应该是哪个呢？

sentences.english: In which of the following ways the handgrip work?
sentences.chinese: 下面哪个是握柄的工作原理？

sentences.english: In which country was Ibrahim Afellay born?
sentences.chinese: 阿费莱出生在哪个国家？

sentences.english: Nobody carries a grudge better than this sign.
sentences.chinese: 没有哪个星座比蝎子更容易产生怨恨情绪了。

sentences.english: What do you think is one thing that should be improved in London?
sentences.chinese: 你觉得伦敦在哪个地方还需要改进？

sentences.english: Which living person do you most admire, and why?
sentences.chinese: 你最敬佩哪个活着的人，为什么？

sentences.english: No other country thinks about food as just fueling up.
sentences.chinese: 没有哪个国家会把食物仅仅看作果腹之用。

sentences.english: The high notes are always harder to play, regardless of the brand of harmonica.
sentences.chinese: 无论是哪个品牌的口琴，高位孔都比较难吹好。

sentences.english: According to the first paragraph, which one of the following statements is TURE of the SeaFalcon?
sentences.chinese: 根据第一段，哪个陈述是关于海鹰正确的描述？
